success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104hap1665702835110.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/hap1665702835110.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/hap1665702835110.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"hap1665702835110\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      More Properties (Window Properties)\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Define additional window properties for the form you are defining.\n </p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"hap1665702835110__p_d9581e1_d9582e1_d9583e1\">The parameters displayed (if any) are initially supplied by Uniface as default parameters for the form. The initialization file for your system can affect these settings (such as <span class=\"ph filepath\">.ini</span>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\"></code> and <span class=\"ph filepath\">.Xdefaults</span>).</p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"hap1665702835110__section_yjv_w1l_5cc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d683204e62\">Fields</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"hap1665702835110__ul_vz1_x1l_5cc\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"hap1665702835110__li_d4436e1_d4437e1_d4438e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"smu1665702835261.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/smu1665702835261.html\" title=\"Specify the platform-specific properties to define.\">Parameter Name</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"hap1665702835110__li_d4439e1_d4440e1_d4441e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ttk1665702833738.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ttk1665702833738.html\" title=\"Specify one or more values for any user-defined or platform-specific properties of a widget or window. Separate multiple values with commas.\">Parameter Value</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"hap1665702835110__section_bgn_y1l_5cc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d683204e89\">How to</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"hap1665702835110__p_d9590e1_d9591e1_d9592e1\">Click <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">New</span> to add a property or\n          <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Delete</span> to delete a property.</p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2528123\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2528123\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "More Properties (Window Properties) Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Sept 21, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 More Properties (Window Properties) Define additional window properties for the form you are defining. The parameters displayed (if any) are initially supplied by Uniface as default parameters for the form. The initialization file for your system can affect these settings (such as .ini and .Xdefaults ). Fields Parameter Name Parameter Value How to Click New to add a property or Delete to delete a property. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}